"versions més noves"

#. type: Plain text
msgid ""
"- 64-bit PAE-enabled kernel with NX-bit and SMP support on hardware that "
"supports it"
msgstr ""
"- Nucli habilitat per PAE de 64 bits amb suport per a NX-bit i SMP al "
